[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about whether test classes should be public, especially if they're nested. I wonder if they really need to avoid direct reflection in tests. Should they reside in a different package than the library? I’m trying to clarify if using Class.getName counts as direct reflection. It seems like it might not be an issue, but I’ll have to be careful with how I organize this. So, it's good to think this through!
